# Send monitoring emails straight to the monitoring host, bypassing the usual mail relay.
# Nagios potentially generates a lot of mail, and we don't want that potentially tripping send quotas.
# Also, monitoring.redradishtech.com is whitelisted on sandboxes that other SMTP destinations are blacklisted.
# jeff@redradishtech.com
# https://superuser.com/questions/749759/postfix-relay-based-on-recepient
transport_maps = hash:/etc/postfix/relay_per_recipient

